#Text=I want to thank you very much .

#Text=Jobs are booming in our country , incomes are soaring , poverty has plummeted , confidence is surging , and we have completely rebuilt the awesome power of a thing called the United States military .
#Text=Every day , for me and for you , it 's promises made , promises kept .
#Text=One of the most important promises I made is right to this era .
#Text=You know , we look at it , it 's the never ending wars in the Middle East .
#Text=We 're taking our soldiers , we 're bringing them back home .
#Text=We 're not law enforcement .
#Text=We 're bringing them back home .
#Text=American troops can not be the policemen for the world , or to create democracy in other nations that frankly probably do n't want it .
#Text=The job of the American military is to secure and defend our country .
#Text=Two days ago , the Unites States signed a deal with the Taliban so that after 19 years of conflict , and very close to 20 , we can finally begin to bring our amazing troops back home .

#Text=And all of the things that we 've done , we 've wiped out the terrorists , we 've done so much , and you know what ?

#Text=As we bring back our troops , we are committed to ensuring that foreign terrorists are denied admission to America in the first place .

#Text=Washington Democrats are trying to politicize the coronavirus , denigrating the noble work of our public health professionals .
#Text=But honestly , not so much anymore .

#Text=And I have to say , with a thriving economy the way it is , and the most advanced health system on earth , America is so resilient , we know what we 're doing , we have the greatest people on earth , the greatest health system on earth .
#Text=We have the greatest health system on earth .
#Text=The renewal of American strength over the last three years means at times of challenge , we are the best prepared to rise to any occasion .
#Text=No country is better equipped than America to handle new threats , and no people are more skilled , talented , tough , or driven than Americans .
#Text=And together , we are in the midst of the great American comeback .
#Text=That 's what it is .
#Text=Last month , we added 225,000 new jobs in January alone .
#Text=That makes seven million jobs since the election .
#Text=We have destroyed the ISIS territorial caliphate , and we killed the founder and leader of ISIS , al - Baghdadi .
#Text=He is dead .
#Text=And we took out the world 's top terrorist , Qasem Soleimani , ending his evil reign on terror forever , Soleimani .

#Text=While the extreme left has been wasting time with vile hoaxes and delusional witch hunts , we have been killing terrorists , creating jobs , raising wages , and lifting up American citizens of every race , religion , color , and creed .
